<div id="review_328356748" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/328356748" />
    <a title="Saba" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/6019262-saba"><img alt="Saba" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1601349487p2/6019262.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/328356748?book_show_action=true">May 11, 2012</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Saba" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Saba" href="/user/show/6019262-saba">Saba</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/6019262-saba?shelf=favorites">favorites</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/6019262-saba?shelf=wishlist">wishlist</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/6019262-saba?shelf=women-suffering-injustice">women-suffering-injustice</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer328356748" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1600889111344424934">This book was AMAZING!! Although &quot;A Walk Across the Sun&quot; is fictional, human trafficking is all too real. This could be easily be an unfortunate young girl&apos;s story. This book really opened my eyes to the &quot;hidden world of sexual violence, where the most valuable prize is the innocence of a child&quot;. I would highly recommend it to everyone. This is truly a groundbreaking debut novel!</span>
  <span id="freeText1600889111344424934" style="display:none">This book was AMAZING!! Although "A Walk Across the Sun" is fictional, human trafficking is all too real. This could be easily be an unfortunate young girl's story. This book really opened my eyes to the "hidden world of sexual violence, where the most valuable prize is the innocence of a child". I would highly recommend it to everyone. This is truly a groundbreaking debut novel!</span>
  <a data-text-id="1600889111344424934" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


